%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20experts%20to%20understand%20why%20women's%20sweaters%20can%20be%20more%20expensive%20than%20men's%20sweaters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDeeper%20discounts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FNfrX2%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Sweater%20prices%20at%20five%20companies%20by%20gender%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ESheng%20Lu%20is%20an%20associate%20professor%20of%20fashion%20and%20apparel%20studies%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Delaware.%20He%20teaches%20courses%20that%20focus%20on%20product%20sourcing%20and%20pricing%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20BI%20that%20companies%20typically%20set%20their%20prices%20based%20on%20the%20cost%20of%20goods%2C%20expected%20gross%20margin%2C%20and%20retail%20reduction%2C%20or%20the%20discount%20they%20expect%20to%20offer%20in%20the%20future.%20Women's%20apparel%20is%20more%20trend-driven%20than%20menswear%20and%20has%20a%20more%20competitive%20market.%20These%20factors%20can%20pressure%20retailers%20to%20heavily%20discount%20women's%20clothing%2C%20Lu%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2Fv2qDj%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Price%20of%20clothing%20item%20by%20gender%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22312%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20anticipate%20more%20discounts%20you%20have%20to%20offer%20during%20the%20selling%20season%2C%20therefore%2C%20they%20price%20their%20products%20higher%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20changing%20trends%2C%20women's%20apparel%20can%20also%20be%20riskier%20to%20sell.%20%26quot%3BThere%20can%20be%20some%20risk%20involved%20in%20predicting%20what%20consumers%20may%20want%2C%26quot%3B%20Lu%20said.%20If%20those%20predictions%20are%20wrong%2C%20retailers%20are%20stuck%20with%20unsold%20inventory%2C%20so%20they%20factor%20this%20risk%20into%20the%20retail%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHigher%20tariffs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2Fg884w%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Price%20per%20clothing%20item%20at%20Abercrombie%20%26amp%3Bamp%3B%20Fitch%20by%20gender%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20clothing%20we%20see%20in%20stores%20today%20is%20imported%20from%20other%20countries%2C%20Lu%20said.%20That%20means%20tariffs%2C%20or%20import%20taxes%2C%20can%20also%20affect%20the%20retail%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELu%20pulled%20import%20data%20for%20this%20story%20from%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Commerce%20and%20the%20US%20International%20Trade%20Commission.%20He%20noticed%20some%20tariff%20prices%20were%20higher%20for%20women's%20apparel%20than%20for%20men's%2C%20though%20it%20didn't%20appear%20to%20be%20systematic%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%202022%20ITC%20data%2C%20several%20categories%20had%20the%20same%20tariffs%20for%20both%20men's%20and%20women's%20clothing%2C%20while%20others%20did%20not.%20For%20example%2C%20men's%20wool%20sweaters%20had%20an%20average%20tariff%20rate%20of%2013.6%25%2C%20while%20women's%20wool%20sweaters%20had%20an%20average%20tariff%20rate%20of%2014.9%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22composite%20image%20of%20sweaters%20folded%20on%20tables%20at%20Abercrombie%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659d6715dcdb354a9855de38%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20women's%20sweater%20at%20Abercrombie%20costs%20%2490.%20A%20men's%20sweater%20at%20Abercrombie%20costs%20%2480.%20Both%20are%20blends%20of%20synthetic%20and%20natural%20fibers.%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Ortakales%20Dawkins%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20some%20commonly%20worn%20clothing%2C%20the%20tariff%20rate%20for%20womenswear%20is%20relatively%20higher%20than%20menswear%2C%26quot%3B%20Lu%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhich%20means%20even%20if%20you%20import%20the%20same%20item%2C%20pay%20the%20same%20price%2C%20for%20womenswear%20you%20have%20to%20pay%20a%20higher%20tariff.%20And%20surely%20retailers%20will%20pass%20over%20these%20tariffs%20to%20consumers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20reason%20for%20the%20discrepancy%20could%20be%20because%20womenswear%20is%20more%20frequently%20imported%20from%20Asian%20countries%20where%20tariffs%20are%20required%2C%20Lu%20said.%20Companies%20can%20avoid%20tariffs%20when%20they%20import%20from%20countries%20where%20the%20US%20has%20free-trade%20agreements%2C%20such%20as%20Mexico%20and%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMore%20complex%20designs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2Ft5E4j%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Price%20per%20clothing%20item%20at%20J.%20Crew%20by%20gender%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20not%20just%20the%20import%20country%20that%20affects%20tariffs.%20Rates%20are%20also%20determined%20by%20the%20material%20content%20and%20style%20details%20of%20a%20garment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFran%20Kozen%20is%20a%20fiber%20science%20and%20apparel%20design%20professor%20at%20Cornell%20University.%20She%20told%20BI%20that%20since%20women's%20styles%20are%20usually%20more%20complex%20than%20men's%20they%20can%20garner%20higher%20tariff%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20embellishments%20and%20things%20that%20are%20put%20onto%20women's%20tops%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20mean%20that%20the%20tariffs%20are%20higher%20on%20those%20than%20on%20a%20plain%20T-shirt%2C%26quot%3B%20Kozen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22composite%20image%20of%20a%20women's%20sweater%20and%20men's%20sweater%20at%20J.%20Crew%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659d6898ec62ab5daf81e260%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20women's%20sweater%20at%20J.%20Crew%20made%20mostly%20from%20polyamide%20and%207%25%20merino%20wool%20sells%20for%20%24178.%20A%20men's%20100%25%20wool%20sweater%20at%20J.%20Crew%20sells%20for%20%24168.%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Ortakales%20Dawkins%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20also%20translates%20to%20the%20overall%20cost%20of%20manufacturing%20the%20garment.%20Women's%20apparel%20follows%20rapidly%20changing%20trend%20cycles%20and%20typically%20offers%20a%20wider%20range%20of%20sizes%20and%20colors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20costs%20brands%20more%20money%20every%20time%20they%20have%20to%20develop%20a%20new%20product%2C%26quot%3B%20Kozen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20also%20be%20more%20difficult%20to%20design%20women's%20garments%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20sizes%2C%20so%20product%20development%20can%20take%20longer%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22composite%20image%20of%20a%20women's%20sweater%20and%20men's%20sweater%20folded%20on%20tables%20at%20J.%20Crew%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659d69976979d7371821a26b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20some%20cases%2C%20women's%20sweaters%20can%20have%20lower%20retail%20prices.%20Take%20these%20100%25%20cashmere%20crewneck%20sweaters%20at%20J.%20Crew.%20The%20women's%20version%20is%20%24118%20and%20the%20men's%20version%20%24138.%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Ortakales%20Dawkins%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMore%20synthetic%20fibers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FmtK1r%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Price%20per%20clothing%20item%20at%20Gap%20by%20gender%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20materials%2C%20women's%20sweaters%20are%20often%20blended%20with%20both%20natural%20and%20synthetic%20materials%20to%20fit%20their%20preferences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWomen%20like%20drapey%2C%20closer%20to%20the%20body%20fitting%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20Kozen%20said.%20%26quot%3BLighter%20weight%20sweaters%20are%20going%20to%20be%20appealing.%26quot%3B%20While%20natural%20fibers%20like%20cotton%20and%20wool%20can%20be%20stiff%2C%20synthetic%20fibers%20add%20softness.%20Men's%20sweaters%20can%20also%20contain%20synthetic%20fibers%20like%20polyester%2C%20she%20said%2C%20but%20it's%20usually%20for%20durability%20and%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESynthetic%20fibers%20also%20make%20it%20possible%20for%20retailers%20to%20keep%20prices%20low%2C%20she%20added%20%E2%80%94%20an%20expectation%20many%20customers%20have%20if%20they%20shop%20frequently%20and%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20latest%20trends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22composite%20image%20of%20a%20women's%20sweater%20and%20a%20men's%20sweater%20hanging%20at%20Gap%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659d67936979d7371821a126%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20women's%20sweater%20at%20Gap%20sells%20for%20%2479.95.%20A%20men's%20sweater%20at%20Gap%20sells%20for%20%2469.95.%20Both%20are%20100%25%20cotton.%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Ortakales%20Dawkins%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20be%20difficult%20to%20find%20high-quality%20sweaters%20when%20shopping%20online%2C%20so%20Bello%20recommends%20shopping%20by%20item%20rather%20than%20brand.%20She%20typically%20looks%20for%20sweaters%20with%2070%25%20to%2085%25%20natural%20fibers%20in%20classic%20styles%20that%20won't%20go%20out%20of%20fashion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20prefer%20materials%20that%20are%20thicker%2C%20so%20they'll%20look%20more%20starchy%20in%20the%20photo%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20if%20something%20looks%20super%20breezy%2C%20you%20can%20kind%20of%20tell%20that%20it's%20thinner%20material.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20that%2C%20she%20suggests%20getting%20something%20%26quot%3Bthat%20you%20think%20you'll%20love%20for%20years%20to%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20And%20if%20it's%20not%20right%2C%20return%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20it%20doesn't%20live%20up%20to%20what%20you're%20imagining%2C%20then%20you're%20not%20going%20to%20reach%20for%20it%20as%20often.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-womens-sweaters-more-expensive-than-mens-sweaters-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705486741000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659c75881c5c7b8c9a0f0696%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-womens-sweaters-more-expensive-than-mens-sweaters-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Brands%20often%20price%20women's%20sweaters%20higher%20than%20men's.%20This%20has%20to%20do%20with%20costs%20like%20tariffs%20and%20discounts%20that%20factor%20into%20the%20retail%20price.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jortakales%40insider.com%20(Jennifer%20Ortakales%20Dawkins%2CNoah%20Sheidlower)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-womens-sweaters-more-expensive-than-mens-sweaters-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Reading%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20Against%20Practices%20in%20Delhi%20University%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F14161808%2FDelhi-university.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20back%20to%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%2C%202020%20and%20read%20it%20all%20over%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20I%3F%20That%2C%20we%20the%20teachers%20and%20students%20in%20higher%20education%20are%20told%2C%20is%20the%20basis%20of%20all%20that%20makes%20up%20for%20the%20changes%20in%20the%20last%20one%20and%20a%20half%20years%3B%20one%20short%20hand%20that%20justifies%20the%20the%20new%20steps%3B%20one%3Cem%3E%20open%20sesame%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20newness%2C%20if%20you%20like!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20%E2%80%9Cfirst%20educational%20policy%20of%20the%2021st%20century%E2%80%9D%2C%20intended%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Coperational%20during%202030-2040%E2%80%9D%2C%20presents%20certain%20aspects%20as%20foundational%20and%20it%20would%20be%20good%20to%20review%20these%20ideas%20against%20the%20steps%20taken%20so%20far%20using%20the%20teaching%20experience%20in%20Delhi%20University%20%E2%80%93%20an%20early%20bird%20and%20thus%20a%20likely%20forerunner%20in%20NEP%20implementation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHolistic%20development%E2%80%9D%20is%20one%20mantra%20in%20the%20NEP.%20The%20NEP%20argues%20against%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20hard%20separation%E2%80%9D%20of%20arts%20and%20sciences%20as%20well%20as%20between%20curricular%20and%20extra-curricular%20activities.%20Student-run%2C%20faculty-mentored%20clubs%20and%20activities%20are%20said%20to%20be%20so%20important%20that%20the%20NEP%20has%20provisions%20for%20funding%20them!%20But%20in%20Delhi%20University%2C%20where%20I%20teach%2C%20the%20NEP%20system%20has%20increased%20the%20number%20of%20courses%20for%20students%2C%20leaving%20them%20in%20the%20class%20room%20practically%20throughout%20the%20day.%20The%20number%20of%20classes%20in%20courses%20has%20been%20reduced%20%E2%80%93%20when%20many%20of%20these%20courses%20were%20taught%20with%20almost%20the%20same%20content%20and%20in%2075%25%20more%20lectures!%20This%20overcrowded%20scheme%20not%20only%20makes%20learning%20rushed%2C%20summary-based%20and%20superfluous%20but%20also%20takes%20away%20the%20time%20for%20student%20activities%2C%20diminishing%20their%20%E2%80%9Cholistic%20development%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NEP%20does%20talk%20about%20its%20aim%20to%20make%20the%20student%20number%20in%20higher%20education%20institutions%203%2C000%2C%20with%20a%20promise%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20student-teacher%20ratio%20will%20not%20be%20too%20high%E2%80%9D%20and%20insisting%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Cphysical%20infrastructure%20and%20appropriate%20resources%20conducive%20for%20learning%E2%80%9D.%20If%20student%20numbers%20are%20increased%20(as%20Delhi%20University%20colleges%20have%20increased%20seats%20up%20to%2020%25)%20without%20increasing%20the%20number%20of%20teachers%20and%20building%20infrastructure%20and%20resources%2C%20it%20goes%20against%20the%20NEP%E2%80%99s%20plan.%20%E2%80%9CQuality%20classroom%20transaction%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20passing%20mention%20in%20the%20document%2C%20there%20lay%20abandoned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMultidisciplinarity%E2%80%9D%20is%20one%20central%20and%20most%20repeated%20NEP%20theme.%20In%20its%20conceptualisation%20of%20a%20Four%20Year%20Undergraduate%20Programme%2C%20a%20student%20has%20multiple%20exit%20options%20the%20NEP%20offers%3A%20after%20one%20year%2C%20certificate%3B%20after%20two%20years%2C%20diploma%3B%20after%20three%20years%2C%20bachelor%E2%80%99s%20degree%3B%20and%20after%20four%2C%20multidisciplinary%20bachelor%E2%80%99s%20programme.%20The%20first%20year%20is%20over%20and%20there%20is%20no%20record%20of%20how%20many%20left%20with%20a%20certificate.%20Whatever%20that%20number%20is%2C%20the%20difficulty%20is%20that%20the%20first%20year%20courses%20haven%E2%80%99t%20been%20formulated%20with%20such%20cohesiveness%20that%20there%20looks%20a%20beginning%2C%20middle%20and%20end%20for%20it%20as%20a%20one%20year%20stand-alone%20entity.%20Under%20the%20category%20of%20Value%20Added%20Courses%20and%20Skill%20Enhancement%20Courses%2C%20a%20number%20of%20courses%20have%20been%20introduced%3A%20any%20department%20can%20teach%20these%20courses%20without%20worrying%20about%20expertise%20and%20specialisation%2C%20caricaturing%20the%20very%20idea%20of%20%E2%80%9Cmultidisciplinarity%E2%80%9D!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTeacher%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20NEP%20proclaims%2C%20%E2%80%9Cis%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20all%20reforms%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cat%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20learning%20process%E2%80%9D%20and%20they%20are%20supposed%20to%20be%20mentors%20as%20well.%20While%20the%20NEP%20talks%20of%20%E2%80%9Ctenure%20track%E2%80%9D%20(a%20sort%20of%20probation)%20and%20%E2%80%9Ctenure%E2%80%9D%20(permanent)%20in%20proper%20American%20university%20terms%2C%20this%20is%20the%20domain%20in%20which%20the%20cruellest%20kind%20of%20exploitation%20has%20come%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20University%E2%80%99s%20ad%20hoc%20appointment%20system%20had%20three%20benefits%3A%20ad%20hoc%20teachers%20were%20paid%20almost%20the%20same%20amount%20as%20that%20of%20an%20entry%20level%20permanent%20staff%20minus%20increments%20and%20some%20allowances%2C%20their%20experience%20counted%20when%20they%20applied%20for%20permanent%20jobs%2C%20for%20their%20promotions%20later%2C%20and%20they%20had%20vacation%20salary%20if%20they%20worked%20on%20the%20last%20and%20first%20day%20of%20the%20vacation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20been%20replaced%20by%20the%20new%20guest%20system%20%E2%80%93%20where%20each%20guest%20can%20only%20handle%20half%20the%20workload%20of%20an%20ad%20hoc%2C%20they%20are%20paid%20by%20the%20teaching%20hour%20which%20effectively%20means%20paid%20only%20for%208%20out%20of%2012%20months%20with%20no%20vacation%20salary%20and%20their%20guest%20teaching%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20count%20as%20teaching%20experience.%20Over-worked%2C%20under-paid%20and%20undocumented%20labour%20of%20young%20minds%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20teacher%20centricism!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20the%20horrible%20backlog%20of%20permanent%20appointments%20in%20Delhi%20University%20created%20another%20issue%3A%20many%20long-serving%20ad%20hocs%2C%20some%20more%20than%20of%20a%20decade%2C%20got%20displaced%20from%20their%20job%2C%20and%20their%20contribution%20to%20the%20growth%20of%20departments%20went%20thanklessly%20unaccounted%20for.%20Due%20to%20the%20fast%20forwarded%20nature%20of%20interviews%2C%20some%20actually%20lasted%20only%20for%20a%20minute%20or%20two%2C%20and%20serious%20allegations%20of%20favouritism%20in%20some%20colleges%20students%20got%20pushed%20into%20staging%20protests%20against%20this%20unfair%20treatment%20of%20teachers%2C%20making%20one%20wonder%20whatever%20happened%20to%20NEP%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cteacher%20centrality%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20assessment%20systems%2C%20the%20suggested%20criterion-based%20grading%20system%20with%20more%20continuous%20and%20comprehensive%20evaluation%2C%20%E2%80%9Cmoving%20away%20from%20high%20stake%20examinations%E2%80%9D%20has%20increased%20the%20internal%20mark%20component.%20Given%20the%20number%20of%20courses%20a%20student%20has%20to%20attend%2C%20the%20number%20of%20graded%20tasks%20in%20a%20semester%20and%20the%20persistent%20bureaucratic%20notions%2C%20teachers%20would%20be%20tripling%20up%20as%20exam%20superintends%2C%20invigilators%20and%20evaluators%2C%20all%20rolled%20into%20one%2C%20for%20most%20of%20the%20teaching%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20NEP%20is%20in%20such%20contrast%20with%20the%20stated%20projects%2C%20who%20is%20to%20be%20blamed%3F%20I%20think%20it%20is%20the%20fault%20of%20professors%20sitting%20in%20on%20the%20highest%20decision-making%20bodies%2C%20such%20as%20the%20academic%20council%20and%20the%20executive%20council%2C%20for%20they%20do%20not%20use%20their%20discerning%20power%2C%20domain%20expertise%20and%20educational%20experience%20ethically%20in%20heralding%20a%20newly%20developed%20policy%20to%20an%20area%20they%20are%20in%20charge%20of.%20Either%20there%20is%20cynical%20resignation%20or%20timid%20collaboration%20with%20some%20policy%20makers%20%E2%80%93%20in%20both%20cases%20they%20are%20not%20doing%20their%20job.%20This%20chasm%20between%20what%20is%20said%20and%20what%20is%20done%20will%20waste%20our%20public%20universities%20into%20a%20demonetised%20state%20%E2%80%93%20the%20inefficiency%20and%20the%20mayhem%20witnessed%20in%20admissions%2C%20course%20content%2C%20academic%20directives%20and%20examination%20process%20in%20the%20last%20one%20and%20a%20year%20have%20started%20demonstrating%20already.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NEP%20concludes%20by%20talking%20about%20the%20need%20to%20have%20comprehensiveness%20in%20implementation%20and%20the%20need%20to%20review%20the%20linkages%20between%20multiple%20parallel%20steps%20and%20in%20such%20a%20task%20is%20undertaken%20with%20its%20implemented%20version%2C%20the%20NEP%20is%20unlikely%20to%20recognise%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20organising%20principles%20of%20the%20NEP%20were%20always%20contested.%20There%20is%20an%20Indian%20story%20in%20education%20which%20is%20the%20basis%20of%20India%20being%20the%20largest%20provider%20of%20skilled%20engineers%20for%20the%20knowledge%20economy%20and%20its%20substantial%20contribution%20to%20the%20global%20academic%20scene.%20This%20immediate%20past%20was%20totally%20hidden%20and%20an%20ancient%20India%20%E2%80%9Cgolden%20age%20narrative%E2%80%9D%20was%20formulated%20to%20redress%20the%20majoritarian%20fears%2C%20concocted%20by%20the%20majoritarian%20political%20propaganda%20of%20fear%20and%20inferiority.%20This%20obsession%20is%20one%20major%20flaw%20of%20the%20NEP.%20Moreover%2C%20its%20deployment%20of%20choice%20and%20freedom%20seem%20to%20address%20consumers%20of%20an%20academic%20mall%20and%20not%20citizens-in-the-making%20of%20a%20republic%20(This%20is%20not%20to%20say%20earlier%20it%20was%20all%20picture%20perfect.%20In%20experience%2C%20the%20shift%20might%20just%20be%20from%20one%20that%20scared%20students%20as%20subjects%20to%20one%20that%20is%20scared%20of%20students%20as%20consumers).%20The%20NEP%E2%80%99s%20secret%20agenda%2C%20those%20who%20disagreed%20maintained%2C%20is%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20withdrawal%20from%20the%20social%20sector%20by%20emptying%20out%20the%20existing%20organisations%20of%20character%20and%20quality%20and%20enabling%20the%20market%20players%20to%20extract%20wealth%20from%20the%20moneyed%20for%20their%20children%E2%80%99s%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20those%20views%20are%20kept%20out%20for%20now%2C%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20the%20NEP%20supporters%20be%20specially%20concerned%2C%20if%20their%20journey%20to%20the%20promised%20land%20of%20Indian%20education%20has%20already%20started%20on%20missteps%2C%20with%20so%20much%20being%20out%20of%20syllabus%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20new%20world%20order%20in%20the%20making%2C%20techno-economic%20givens%2C%20insights%20in%20educational%20philosophy%20and%20psychology%2C%20generational%20conflicts%20and%20paradigm%20shifts%20accelerated%20by%20the%20pandemic%20and%20the%20environmental%20scene%2C%20nobody%20will%20say%20our%20educational%20practices%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20need%20revision.%20Indian%20educational%20system%E2%80%99s%20reach%2C%20in%20spite%20of%20its%20socialist%20proclamations%20till%201990s%20or%20a%20mixed%20situation%20thereafter%2C%20went%20beyond%20feudal%2C%20upper%20caste%2C%20metropolitan%20and%20plutocratic%20constraints%20only%20in%20exceptions%20and%20that%20does%20need%20to%20be%20addressed%20and%20corrected.%20But%20all%20these%20require%20an%20inclusive%20and%20egalitarian%20vision%20for%20the%20future%2C%20a%20plan%20that%20can%20actualise%20it%20and%20an%20institutional%20system%20that%20can%20perform%20this%20script%20with%20understanding%20and%20rigour%20%E2%80%93%20bulldozing%20of%20the%20existing%20institutional%20structures%20for%20the%20spectacle%20of%20old%20in%20the%20guise%20of%20the%20new%20can%E2%80%99t%20even%20begin%20to%20do%20it.%20What%20falls%20through%20the%20cracks%20of%20NEP%20theory%20and%20practice%20is%20the%20future%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20is%20like%20that%20of%20Trishanku%3Cem%3E%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20Ikshwaku%20king%20sent%20to%20heaven%20alive%20with%20the%20blessing%20of%20a%20powerful%20human-sage%20but%20was%20stopped%20without%20getting%20entry%20by%20the%20enraged%20chief%20of%20god.%20The%20king%20hanging%20in%20the%20sky%2C%20struggling%20in%20the%20neither-here-nor-here%20of%20empty%20air%20is%20a%20suitable%20but%20sad%20metaphor%20for%20what%20Indian%20higher%20education%20scene%20is%20living%20through%3A%20one%20that%20we%20need%20to%20take%20urgent%20notice%20of%20but%2C%20as%20a%20people%2C%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20to%20get%20accustomed%20to!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EN.P.%20Ashley%20teaches%20English%20at%20St.%20Stephen%E2%80%99s%20College%2C%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705486637000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F14161808%2FDelhi-university.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Freading-the-national-education-policy-against-practices-in-delhi-university%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20implementation%20of%20the%20NEP%20is%20in%20contrast%20with%20its%20stated%20projects.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3