ained%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fg20-pollution-curbs-behind-delay-in-restarting-runway-dial-to-ministry-of-civil-aviation-9112556%2F%5C%22%3Ea%20compressed%20timeline%20post-G20%20Summit%20in%20September%20and%20pollution-related%20curbs%3C%2Fa%3E%20imposed%20by%20the%20Delhi%20government%20posed%20challenges%20to%20completing%20the%20project%20within%20the%20stipulated%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20implementation%20of%20GRAP%20IV%20norms%2C%20due%20to%20pollution%20concerns%2C%20disrupted%20the%20supply%20chain%20for%20civil%20works%2C%20the%20airport%20operator%20said.%20GRAP%20IV%20restrictions%2C%20which%20came%20into%20effect%20on%20November%205%20last%20year%2C%20banned%20the%20entry%20of%20polluting%20vehicles%20from%20other%20states%20in%20Delhi%20in%20addition%20to%20other%20curbs%20to%20combat%20the%20poor%20air%20quality%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDIAL%20also%20highlighted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fg20-pollution-curbs-behind-delay-in-restarting-runway-dial-to-ministry-of-civil-aviation-9112556%2F%5C%22%3Edelays%20in%20the%20supply%20of%20runway%20lights%3C%2Fa%3E%20citing%20supply%20chain%20complexities%20and%20unexpected%20challenges%20during%20the%20cable-laying%20process%2C%20including%20duct%20blockages.%20Despite%20these%20challenges%2C%20DIAL%20has%20assured%20the%20ministry%20that%20it%20will%20meet%20the%20January%2019%20deadline%20for%20the%20project%E2%80%99s%20completion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ongoing%20re-carpeting%20work%20pertains%20to%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20International%20Airport%E2%80%99s%20(IGIA)%20second%20runway%2C%20known%20as%2028%2F10.%20Once%20completed%2C%20the%20airport%20authority%20will%20initiate%20steps%20to%20make%20the%20runway%20CAT%20III%20compliant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECAT%20III%20compliance%20allows%20for%20landing%20in%20very%20low%20visibility%20conditions%2C%20such%20as%20fog%2C%20rain%2C%20or%20snow.%20Currently%2C%20the%20Delhi%20airport%20has%20one%20CAT%20III%20compliant%20runway%2C%2029L%2F11R%2C%20closer%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccity%20side%E2%80%9D%20or%20Gurgaon.%20The%20newest%20runway%2C%2011L%2F29R%2C%20is%20only%20partially%20CAT%20III%20compliant%20and%20is%20awaiting%20certification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20re-carpeting%20is%20finished%2C%20the%20Directorate%20General%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%20(DGCA)%20will%20conduct%20an%20inspection%20to%20identify%20any%20necessary%20changes.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fg20-pollution-curbs-behind-delay-in-restarting-runway-dial-to-ministry-of-civil-aviation-9112556%2F%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20DGCA%20inspection%20has%20already%20been%20carried%20out%20on%20January%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20flights%20have%20been%20disrupted%20over%20the%20past%20few%20days%20because%20of%20fog%20in%20north%20India.%20In%20new%20rules%20to%20tackle%20the%20airport%20chaos%2C%20the%20aviation%20ministry%20has%20asked%20airlines%20to%20cancel%20flights%20delayed%20beyond%20three%20hours%2C%20NDTV%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fco-passenger-on-indigo-flight-shares-what-happened-before-man-slapped-pilot-4872271%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705484671000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F17133238%2FSculpture_of_hasta_mudras_at_Indira_Gandhi_International_Airport.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fflight-delays-maintenance-setback-at-delhi-airport-runway-over-g20-pollution-curbs%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20compressed%20timeline%20post-G20%20Summit%20in%20September%20and%20pollution-related%20curbs%20imposed%20by%20the%20Delhi%20government%20posed%20challenges%20to%20completing%20the%20project%20within%20the%20stipu