20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20an%20engineer%20managed%20to%20unlock%20the%20door.%20By%20then%2C%20he%20had%20been%20confined%20for%20more%20than%20an%20hour.%20The%20flier%2C%20SpiceJet%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20was%20provided%20medical%20attention%20soon%20after%20rescue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%2016%20January%2C%20a%20passenger%20unfortunately%20got%20stuck%20inside%20the%20lavatory%20for%20about%20an%20hour%20on%20SpiceJet%20flight%20operating%20from%20Mumbai%20to%20Bengaluru%2C%20while%20the%20aircraft%20was%20airborne%20due%20to%20a%20malfunction%20in%20the%20door%20lock%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20statement%20from%20the%20airlines%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThroughout%20the%20journey%2C%20our%20crew%20provided%20assistance%20and%20guidance%20to%20the%20passenger.%20Upon%20arrival%2C%20an%20engineer%20opened%20the%20lavatory%20door%2C%20and%20the%20passenger%20received%20immediate%20medical%20support%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpiceJet%20has%20expressed%20regret%20and%20apologised%20for%20the%20inconvenience%20to%20the%20passenger%20and%20said%20it%20will%20refund%20the%20full%20airfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705484520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F76g923g8_spicejet-note_625x300_17_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fspicejet-crews-do-not-panic-note-to-passenger-trapped-in-plane-toilet-4878400%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20was%20business%20as%20usual%20for%20the%20SpiceJet%20crew%20onboard%20a%20Mumbai-Bengaluru%20flight%20yesterday%20till%20they%20realised%20that%20a%20passenger%20was%20trapped%20inside%20the%20toilet.%20The%20crew%20found%20that%20the%20door%20lock%20had%20malfunctioned%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fspicejet-crews-do-not-panic-note-to-passenger-trapped-in-plane-toilet-4878400%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2