gers%20Ron%20DeSantis%20and%20Nikki%20Haley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-china-taiwan-lai-ching-te-real-nightmare-scenario-analyst-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705483549000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a7997143bb77284b9d9bf5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-china-taiwan-lai-ching-te-real-nightmare-scenario-analyst-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trump's%20unpredictability%2C%20combined%20with%20a%20defiant%20DPP%20under%20Lai%20Ching-te%2C%20could%20spell%20trouble%20for%20Beijing%2C%20Rorry%20Daniels%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mloh%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Loh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-china-taiwan-lai-ching-te-real-nightmare-scenario-analyst-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Supporters%20Greet%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20With%20%26quot%3BVP%26quot%3B%20Chants%2C%20Trump%20Says%20This%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20he%20withdrew%20from%20the%202024%20US%20presidential%20race%2C%20Indian-American%20entrepreneur%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20received%20an%20enthusiastic%20welcome%20from%20Donald%20Trump's%20supporters%20while%20he%20endorsed%20his%20former%20rival%20and%20ex-US%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2038-year-old%20Republican%2C%20who%20quit%20after%20he%20failed%20to%20make%20a%20mark%20in%20the%20first%20US%20election%20test%20in%20Iowa%2C%20was%20greeted%20with%20chants%20of%20%26quot%3BVP%2C%20VP%2C%20VP%26quot%3B%20after%20he%20joined%20Trump%20on%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EBREAKING%3A%20Trump%20crowd%20chants%20%26quot%3BVP%20VP%20VP%26quot%3B%20after%20V