Courtesy%20of%20Billy%20O'Connor%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWorking%20as%20a%20caretaker%20isn't%20a%20holiday%20job%2C%20the%20owners%20say%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Great%20Blasket%20Island%20was%20home%20to%20a%20small%20fishing%20community%20until%20residents%20were%20evacuated%20to%20mainland%20Ireland%20in%201953%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irishtimes.com%2Flife-and-style%2Fpeople%2Fthe-last-of-the-blasket-evacuees-we-weren-t-great-mixers-on-the-mainland-1.1831611%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20The%20Irish%20Times.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Extreme%20weather%20conditions%20made%20it%20difficult%20for%20the%20community%20to%20continue%20living%20on%20the%20island%2C%20and%20no%20permanent%20residents%20now%20live%20on%20the%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EO'Connor's%20grandfather%20and%20granduncle%20purchased%20five%20cottages%20on%20the%20island%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Frenovation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erenovated%3C%2Fa%3E%20them%20in%20the%201970s%2C%20the%20couple%20told%20BI.%20Since%202014%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20been%20running%20tours%20and%20guesthouses%20on%20the%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20refurbished%20cottages%20the%20caretakers%20operate%20are%20painted%20white%20and%20have%20black%20tiled%20roofs.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.greatblasketisland.net%2Faccommodation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enightly%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%20start%20from%20130%20euros%2C%20or%20%24141%2C%20per%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20caretakers'%20jobs%20will%20include%20checking%20guests%20in%2C%20serving%20tea%20and%20coffee%20to%20visitors%2C%20cleaning%20the%20cottages%2C%20and%20getting%20them%20ready%20for%20the%20next%20guests%2C%20The%20Great%20Blasket%20Island%20Experience%20shared%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.greatblasketisland.net%2Fjob%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejob%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20followed%20up%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgbisland%2Fstatus%2F1744778816570970192%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%20on%20X%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20January%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20looking%20for%20hardworking%2C%20responsible%20and%20trustworthy%20duo%20that%20have%20great%20people%20skills%20and%20initiative.%20Please%20be%20aware%20this%20is%20not%20a%20holiday%20job.%20The%20season%20can%20get%20VERY%20busy%20and%20you%20will%20be%20on%20your%20feet%20for%20most%20of%20the%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20wrote.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20accommodation%2C%20caretakers%20are%20provided%20the%20main%20bedroom%20above%20the%20coffee%20shop%2C%20and%20all%20meals%20will%20be%20provided%2C%20per%20the%20job%20post.%20But%20things%20like%20alcohol%2C%20toiletries%2C%20and%20travel%20expenses%20are%20to%20be%20covered%20by%20the%20caretakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20declined%20to%20share%20with%20BI%20how%20much%20the%20caretakers%20would%20be%20paid%20for%20working%20on%20the%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22inside%20a%20cottage%20on%20great%20blasket%20island%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a7529edcdb354a98581422%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EInside%20one%20of%20the%20cottages%20for%20rent%20on%20Great%20Blasket%20Island.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Billy%20O'Connor%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20restrictions%20on%20age%20or%20nationality%20as%20long%20as%20they're%20physically%20fit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECompetition%20for%20the%20role%20is%20fierce%2C%20the%20couple%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20year%20we%20advertised%20the%20caretakers'%20role%20we%20received%20Approx%2040%2C000%20application%20emails%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20couple%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20first%20adverti