s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThankfully%2C%20we%20have%20had%20really%20positive%20experiences%20with%20all%20our%20caretakers%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fremote-ireland-island-great-blasket-hotel-job-caretaker-guest-house-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705481891000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a633f743bb77284b9d363c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fremote-ireland-island-great-blasket-hotel-job-caretaker-guest-house-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Some%2040%2C000%20people%20previously%20applied%20for%20the%20role%20of%20caretaker%20on%20Great%20Blasket%20Island%20in%20Ireland%2C%20Billy%20O'Connor%20and%20Alice%20Murphy%20told%20BI.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mdescalsota%40insider.com%20(Marielle%20Descalsota)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A38%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fremote-ireland-island-great-blasket-hotel-job-caretaker-guest-house-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ramayan%20legends%20reach%20Ayodhya%20ahead%20of%20Ram%20Mandir%20grand%20event%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705481732000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106923801%2Cimgsize-44532.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Framayan-legends-arun-govil-deepika-chikhlia-and-sunil-lahri-reach-ayodhya-ahead-of-the-grand-inauguration-of-ram-mandir-watch%2Farticleshow%2F106923727.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Arun%20Govil%2C%20Deepika%20Chikhlia%2C%20and%20Sunil%20Lahri%2C%20popularly%20known%20for%20their%20roles%20in%20Ramayan%2C%20have%20arrived%20in%20Ayodhya%20for%20the%20grand%20inauguration%20of%20Ram%20Mandir%20on%20January%2022.%20They%20shared%20glimpses%20of%20their%20journey%20on%20social%20media%2C%20wearing%20traditional%20outfits.%20People%20are%20excited%20to%20see%20them%20at%20the%20event.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22etimes.in%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%222%2C%20Including%20Minor%2C%20Gored%20To%20Death%20During%20Jallikattu%20Bull%20Taming%20Festival%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwo%20people%2C%20including%20a%20boy%2C%20were%20gored%20to%20death%20by%20bulls%20at%20a%20Jallikattu%20venue%20at%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20Sivaganga%20district%20today.%20According%20to%20police%2C%20the%20tragic%20incident%20at%20Siravayal%20near%20Madurai%20did%20not%20take%20place%20during%20the%20Jallikattu%20event%2C%20but%20after%20the%20run%20when%20the%20bull%20owners%20had%20gathered%20to%20collect%20their%20animals.%20At%20that%20point%2C%20police%20said%2C%20the%20bulls%20ran%20helter-skelter%20and%20the%20victims%20were%20gored%20to%20death%20by%20separate%20animals.%C2%A0%C2%A0A%20total%20of%20186%20bulls%20were%20part%20of%20this%20Jallikattu%20event%20that%20is%20still%20underway%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20raises%20question%20marks%20on%20the%20safety%20measures%20in%20place%20for%20the%20bull-taming%20sport.%20Safety%20norms%20mandated%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20include%20double%20barricading%20of%20the%20entire%20arena%20and%20steps%20to%20ensure%20no%20animal%20injures%20spectators.%20Injuries%20have%20been%20reported%20from%20other%20Jallikattu%20venues%20too.%C2%A0At%20least%2060%20people%20were%20injured%20yesterday%20at%20Palamedu%20in%20Madurai%20district.%20The%20event%20is%20underway%20at%20Alanganallur%2C%20seen%20as%20the%20capital%20of%20Jallikattu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETraditionally%20played%20in%20several%20parts%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20during%20the%20Pongal%20festival%2C%20Jallikattu%20has%20been%20the%20subject%20of%20heated%20debates%20and%20protracted%20legal%20battles%20for%20years%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnimal%20rights%20organisations%20have%20called%20for%20a%20ban%20on%20the%20sport%2C%20citing%20a%20risk%20of%20injury%20to%20both%20the%20participants%20and%20the%20bull.%20However%2C%20any%20move%20to%20prohibit%20the%20sport%20has%20sparked%20widespread%20protests%20by%20its%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJallikattu%20was%20first%20banned%20following%20a%20Madras%20High%20Court%20order%20in%202006.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20in%202014%20barred%20the%20sport%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20animal%20cruelty.%20Following%20protests%2C%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20temporarily%20lifted%20the%20ban%20in%202017.%20It%20then%20amended%20laws%20governing%20the%20sport.%20This%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20another%20legal%20battle%2C%20with%20animal%20rights%20groups%20challenging%20the%20legislation%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20arguments%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20called%20Jallikattu%20%26quot%3Bnot%20merely%20an%20act%20of%20entertainment%20or%20amusement%20but%20an%20event%20with%20great%20historic%2C%20cultural%20and%20religious%20value%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20upheld%20the%20state%20government's%20law%20allowing%20'Jallikattu'%20events.%20A%20five-judge%20constitution%20bench%20headed%20by%20Justice%20KM%20Joseph%20stated%20that%20when%20the%20legislature%20has%20declared%20'Jallikattu'%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20cultural%20heritage%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20the%20judiciary%20cannot%20take%20a%20different%20view%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20stated%20in%20its%20order%20that%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Cruelty%20to%20Animals%20(Tamil%20Nadu%20Amendment)%20Act%2C%202017%20%26quot%3Bsubstantially%20minimises%20cruelty%20to%20animals%20in%20sports%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Act%20includes%20several%20measures%20to%20ensure%20the%20welfare%20of%20bulls%2C%20such%20as%20requiring%20them%20to%20be%20properly%20fed%20and%20watered%2C%20and%20prohibiting%20the%20use%20of%20any%20sharp%20objects%20or%20chemicals%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Jallikattu%20events%2C%20a%20raging%20bull%20is%20released%20into%20a%20crowd.%20Multiple%20participants%20then%20try%20to%20grab%20its%20hump%20and%20hang%20on%20to%20it%20in%20their%20attempts%20to%20being%20the%20animal%20to%20a%20stop.%20Prizes%20such%20as%20cars%2C%20bikes%20and%20gold%20coins%20are%20up%20for%20the%20grabs%20at%20many%20of%20these%20contests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705481640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-01%2Fnfn054u8_jallikattu-pti_625x300_18_January_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2-including-minor-gored-to-death-during-jallikattu-bull-taming-festival-4878866%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20spectators%2C%20including%20a%20boy%2C%20were%20gored%20to%20death%20by%20bulls%20during%20a%20Jallikattu%20event%20at%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20Sivaganga%20district%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2-including-minor-gored-to-death-during-jallikattu-bull-taming-festival-4878866%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2-including-minor-gored-to-death-during-jallikattu-bull-taming-festival-4878866%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2-including-minor-gored-to-death-during-jallikattu-bull-taming-festival-4878866%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Child%20actors%20who%20SHOCKED%20with%20their%20transformation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705481630000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106923757%2Cimgsize-58514.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fweb-stories%2Favantika-vandanapu-to-swini-khara-child-actors-who-shocked-us-with-their-transformation-photos%2F