nvestment%20leadership%2C%20procurement%20leadership%2C%20sustainable%20development%2C%20incubation%2C%20mentorship%20services%2C%20innovation%2C%20and%20best%20institution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerala%20has%20registered%205%2C000%20startups%20under%20the%20KSUM%2C%20with%20250%20of%20them%20entering%20the%20market%2C%20and%20over%20100%20being%20run%20by%20women%20entrepreneurs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20boasts%2050%20incubators%20across%20its%2014%20districts%20and%20actively%20promotes%20awareness%20programmes%20and%20projects%20to%20mobilise%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKSUM%2C%20established%20in%202006%20by%20the%20Kerala%20government%2C%20focuses%20on%20entrepreneurship%20development%20and%20incubation%20activities%20in%20the%20state%2C%20with%20a%20significant%20presence%20in%20renewable%20energy%2C%20eco-sustainability%2C%20climate%20change%2C%20and%20rural%20development%20startups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%20was%20recognised%20as%20%E2%80%98Leader%E2%80%99%20in%20the%202021%20ranking%2C%20which%20was%20the%20third%20edition.%20In%20the%20first%20two%20editions%2C%20the%20state%20was%20categorised%20in%20the%20bottom-most%20category%20of%20%E2%80%98Emerging%20Ecosystem%E2%80%99%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftn-recognised-as-best-performer-in-states-startup-ranking-2022%2Farticle67745135.ece%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3EHindu%20BusinessLine%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705480052000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fkerala-karnataka-tamil-nadu-himachal-gujarat-are-best-performing-states-for-startup-development%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Telangana%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Odisha%2C%20Punjab%2C%20and%20Rajasthan%20have%20been%20classified%20as%20the%20top-performing%20states.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fkerala-karnataka-tamil-