20secret.%20When%20it%20is%20not%20a%20public%20outing%2C%20they%20are%20always%20discreet%20when%20they%20are%20together%20and%20ensure%20they%20are%20not%20seen%20together%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkhushi-kapoor-and-vedang-raina-alleged-couples-relationship-status-revealed%2Farticleshow%2F106922151.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Movements%20and%20Yatras%20Sustain%20Democratic%20Spirit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F17132803%2FGD9-geSbEAE9vMn.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20massive%20propaganda%20and%20mobilisation%20for%C2%A0%3Cspan%3ERam%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0Temple%20inauguration%20on%20January%2022%20is%20on%20and%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20introspect%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20democratic%20and%20secular%20ethos.%20Soon%20after%20we%20got%20independence%20there%20was%20a%20demand%20from%20some%20quarters%20that%20the%20Somnath%20Temple%2C%20plundered%20by%20Mahmood%20Ghazni%20in%20the%2011th%20century%2C%20be%20restored%20by%20the%20government.%20Nehru%20wrote%20that%20%E2%80%9Che%20and%20Patel%20also%20approached%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20for%20the%20reconstruction%20of%20the%20temple%2C%20but%20Gandhi%20was%20of%20the%20view%20that%20the%20government%20itself%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fc965b30c-0d3c-4b83-814e-abb505ebbd23%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fc965b30c-0d3c-4b83-814e-abb505ebbd23%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1705552690143000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0K14RyndmtFIyTvZcOtrDo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshould%20not%20make%20any%20contribution%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20the%20form%20of%20money%20for%20the%20same.%E2%80%9D%20On%20similar%20lines%20Nehru%20advised%20Rajendra%20Prasad%20not%20to%20inaugurate%20the%20temple%20in%20his%20official%20capacity%20as%20the%20President%20of%20India.%20On%20his%20part%2C%20Nehru%20went%20on%20to%20build%20%E2%80%98Temples%20of%20Modern%20India%E2%80%99%3A%20dams%2C%20public%20sector%20industries%2C%20health%20infrastructure%2C%20educational%20and%20research%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20%E2%80%98one%20person%20one%20vote%E2%80%99%2C%20social%20movements%20of%20workers%2C%20peasants%20and%20other%20sections%20of%20society%20boosted%20democratic%20values.%20Barring%20the%20interlude%20of%20the%20Emergency%2C%20the%20country%20moved%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20gradually%20strengthening%20democratic%20norms%20till%20the%20temple%20movement%20undermined%20the%20very%20%E2%80%98idea%20of%20India%E2%80%99%20which%20had%20emerged%20with%20the%20freedom%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20well%20planned%20demolition%20of%20the%20Babri%20Mosque%20on%20December%206%2C%201992%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20the%20grand%20%3Cspan%3ERam%3C%2Fspan%3E%20temple%20which%20is%20coming%20up%20now.%20The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20has%20not%20only%20focused%20on%20emotive%20issues%20but%20has%20also%20been%20restricting%20the%20democratic%20spaces%20of%20the%20country.%20Overall%2C%20as%20emotive%20issues%20rule%20the%20roost%2C%20aspirations%20for%20better%20living%20conditions%20are%20bypassed%20by%20the%20government.%20We%20are%20living%20in%20dismal%20times%20where%20rising%20prices%20and%20worsening%20indices%20of%20livelihood%20are%20breaking%20the%20back%20of%20average%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhere%20is%20the%20hope%20for%20a%20better%20future%3F%20Some%20glimpses%20of%20our%20latent%20democratic%20strengths%20have%20been%20seen%20in%20the%20past%20few%20years.%20As%20the%20three%20oppressive%20farm%20laws%20were%20introduced%2C%20farmers%20in%20large%20numbers%20marched%20to%20Delhi%20and%20stayed%20put%20for%20months%2C%20sacrificing%20nearly%20600%20of%20their%20colleagues%20in%20the%20struggle.%20Their%20victory%20prove%20that%20democratic%20movements%20can%20still%20shape%20the%20future%20of%20the%20society.%20Then%20we%20saw%20the%20shrewd%20move%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20in%20the%20form%20of%20the%20CAA%2C%20NRC%20to%20disenfranchise%20a%20large%20section%20of%20Muslim%20population.%20Against%20this%20we%20saw%20the%20remarkable%20Shaheen%20Bagh%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F17171339%2FScreen-Shot-2020-03-17-at-5.13.15-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221049%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F17171339%2FScreen-Shot-2020-03-17-at-5.13.15-PM.png%201049w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F17171339%2FScreen-Shot-2020-03-17-at-5.13.15-PM-300x183.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F17171339%2FScreen-Shot-2020-03-17-at-5.13.15-PM-1024x625.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-442023%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EShaheen%20Bagh%20on%20March%2010.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40UmarKhalidJNU%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20summation%20of%20the%20anguish%20of%20people%20came%20up%20in%20the%20form%20of%20%E2%80%98Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%E2%80%99%20(Unite%20India%20March)%20a%20year%20ago.%20It%20gave%20the%20message%20of%20unity%20of%20the%20country%2C%20cutting%20across%20different%20religions%20and%20ethnicities.%20It%20transformed%20the%20social%20atmosphere%20of%20despondency%20into%20one%20of%20hope%20and%20drew%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20nation%20towards%20the%20real%20issues%20of%20the%20society%2C%20the%20issues%20related%20to%20hunger%2C%20shelter%20and%20employment%20among%20others.%20The%20response%20of%20people%20was%20as%20if%20they%20had%20been%20waiting%20for%20such%20an%20event%20to%20happen%20so%20that%20they%20can%20express%20their%20pain%20and%20deprivations%20in%20a%20democratic%20way.%20The%20hope%20for%20the%20inclusive%20society%20with%20earthly%20needs%20got%20rekindled%20and%20a%20new%20ground%20for%20national%20dialogue%20emerged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20did%20make%20its%20mark%20but%20the%20communal%20forces%20have%20created%20a%20very%20efficient%20machinery%20for%20spreading%20their%20divisive%20propaganda%20on%20issues%20which%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20real%20problems%20of%20the%20people.%20So%20the%C2%A0%3Cspan%3ERam%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0Temple%20inauguration%20is%20being%20projected%20as%20an%20event%20on%20par%20with%20India%E2%80%99s%20independence%20day.%20All%20wings%20of%20the%20RSS%20combine%20are%20putting%20their%20energies%20into%20mobilising%20the%20people%20to%20take%20part%20in%20programs%20around%20the%C2%A0%3Cspan%3ERam%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Temple%20inauguration.%20Buses%20and%20extra%20trains%20are%20in%20the%20offing%20to%20help%20divert%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20attention%20to%C2%A0%3Cspan%3ERam%3C%2Fspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20one%20is%20waiting%20for%20January%2022%20%E2%80%93%20when%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20will%20officiate%20at%20the%20ceremony%20in%20Ayodhya%20%E2%80%93%20another%20event%20is%20already%20underway.%20This%20is%20the%20%E2%80%98Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%E2%80%99%2C%20from%20Manipur%20to%20Mumbai%2C%20which%20will%20run%20from%20January%2014%20to%20March%2020.%20This%20hybrid%20(foot%20and%20bus)%20yatra%20began%20from%20Manipur%2C%20the%20state%20neglected%20by%20the%20Union%20Government%20despite%20suffering%20from%20ethnic%20violence%20for%20over%20seven%20months.%20The%20response%20to%20the%20yatra%20from%20the%20people%20of%20Manipur%20has%20been%20overwhelming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20yatra%20is%20going%20to%20focus%20on%20%3Cem%3Enyay%3C%2Fem%3E%20(justice)%20as%20we%20see%20injustice%20all%20around.%20The%20Yatra%E2%80%99s%20focus%20is%20on%20unemployment%2C%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20issues%2C%20rising%20poverty%2C%20the%20dignity%20of%20women%20and%20the%20rights%20of%20Adivasis.%20This%20is%20probably%20the%20best%20possible%20way%20to%20highlight%20the%20issues%20of%20people%20in%20a%20democratic%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20most%20of%20the%20media%20is%20enthralled%20by%20the%20%3Cspan%3ERam%3C%2Fspan%3E%20temple%20issue%2C%20the%20need%20is%20to%20spread%20the%20message%20of%20this%20yatra%20far%20and%20wide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0%3Cspan%3ERam%3C%2Fspan%3E%20temple%20issue%20is%20the%20agenda%20of%20RSS-BJP%20and%20is%20strengthening%20authoritarian%20politics%3B%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20is%20articulating%20values%20related%20to%20Constitutional%20morality.%20It%20should%20not%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20program%20of%20any%20particular%20party.%20It%20is%20the%20summation%20of%20the%20expressions%20of%20the%20needs%20and%20rights%20of%20diverse%20sections%20of%20society.%20It%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20retrieve%20and%20expand%20democratic%20space%20from%20the%20jaws%20of%20communal%20polarisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ERam%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EPuniyani%3C%2Fspan%3E%20is%20president%2C%20Centre%20of%20Study%20of%20Society%20and%20Secularism%20and%20has%20written%20several%20books%20including%20%3C%2Fem%3ECommunal%20Politics%3A%20Facts%20Versus%20Myths%2C%20Deconstructing%20Terrorist%20Violence%2C%20Indian%20Nationalism%20versus%20Hindu%20Nationalism%20%3Cem%3Eand%3C%2Fem%3E%20Caste%20and%20Communalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20updated%20and%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%20click%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705478714000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F17132803%2FGD9-geSbEAE9vMn.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmovements-and-yatras-sustain-democratic-spirit%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20retrieve%20and%20expand%20democratic%20space%20from%20the%20jaws%20of%20communal%20polarisation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmovements-and-yatras-sustain-democratic-spirit%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Centre%20for%20Policy%20Research%20Calls%20MHA's%20Decision%20to%20Cancel%20FCRA%20Registration%20'Incomprehensible'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F09%2F07154303%2FUntitled-design-4-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20has%20cancelled%20the%20Foreign%20Contribution%20Regulation%20Act%20(FCRA)%20registration%20of%20the%20Centre%20for%20Policy%20Research%20(CPR)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fhome-ministry-cancels-fcra-registration-of-centre-for-policy-research%2Farticle67746190.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20registration%20had%20earlier%20been%20suspended%20in%20February%202023.%20The%20policy%20think-tank%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwe-are-in-complete-compliance-with-the-law-cpr-on-fcra-registration-suspension%5C%22%3Ehad%20said%20at%20the%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20is%20in%20complete%20compliance%20with%20all%20laws%20and%20was%20working%20with%20the%20authorities%20to%20have%20the%20license%20issue%20resolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20on%20January%2010%2C%20CPR%20learnt%20that%20its%20FCRA%20registration%20now%20stands%20cancelled.%20President%20of%20the%20organisation%20Yamini%20Aiyar%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20CPR%20is%20weighing%20its%20options%20on%20how%20it%20can%20seek%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20released%20on%20Wednesday%20(January%2017)%2C%20Aiyar%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20basis%20of%20this%20decision%20is%20incomprehensible%20and%20disproportionate%2C%20and%20some%20of%20the%20reasons%20given%20challenge%20the%20very%20basis%20of%20the%20functioning%20of%20a%20research%20institution.%20This%20includes%20the%20publication%20on%20our%20website%20of%20policy%20reports%20emanating%20from%20our%20research%20being%20equated%20with%20current%20affairs%20programming.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20tenure%20of%20our%20suspension%2C%20we%20sought%20and%20obtained%20interim%20redress%20from%20the%20honourable%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20seek%20recourse%20in%20all%20avenues%20possible.%20This%20cancellation%20comes%20after%20a%20decision%20to%20suspend%20the%20FCRA%20status%20in%20February%202023.%20These%20actions%20followed%20an%20Income%20Tax%20%E2%80%9Csurvey%E2%80%9D%20that%20took%20place%20in%20September%202022.%20The%20actions%20have%20had%20a%20debilitating%20impact%20on%20the%20institution%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20function%20by%20choking%20all%20sources%20of%20funding.%20This%20has%20undermined%20the%20institution%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20pursue%20its%20well%20established%20objective%20of%20producing%20high%20quality%2C%20globally%20recognised%20research%20on%20policy%20matters%2C%20which%20it%20has%20been%20recognised%20for%20over%20its%2050%20years%E2%80%99%20existence.%20During%20this%20time%20the%20institution%20has%20been%20home%20to%20some%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20most%20distinguished%20academics%2C%20diplomats%20and%20policymakers%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20continues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCPR%20is%20a%2050-year-old%20institution%20that%20has%20a%20proud%20legacy%20of%20deep%20contributions%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20policy%20making%20ecosystem%2C%20and%20over%20the%20past%20five%20decades%20has%20been%20home%20to%20many%20distinguished%20faculty%2C%20researchers%20and%20members%20of%20the%20board.%20CPR%20firmly%20reiterates%20that%20it%20is%20in%20complete%20compliance%20with%20the%20law%2C%20and%20has%20been%20cooperating%20fully%20and%20exhaustively%20at%20every%20step%20of%20the%20process.%20We%20remain%20steadfast%20in%20our%20belief%20that%20this%20matter%20will%20be%20resolved%20in%20line%20with%20constitutional%20values%20and%20guarantees%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20concludes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%202022%2C%20the%20Income%20Tax%20Department%20had%20carried%20out%20searches%20at%20CPR%E2%80%99s%20offices.%20Other%20NGOs%2C%20including%20Oxfam%20India%2C%20were%20also%20targeted.%20Since%20then%2C%20CPR%20said%2C%20it%20has%20responded%20to%20all%20the%20notices%20served%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20order%20dated%20February%2027%2C%202023%2C%20the%20MHA%20had%20alleged%20that%20CPR%20has%20been%20using%20its%20FCRA%20funds%20for%20purposes%20other%20than%20the%20educational%20programmes%20for%20which%20the%20licence%20was%20granted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcademics%20and%20researchers%20from%20across%20the%20world%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdangerous-precedent-international-scholars-researchers-on-cprs-fcra-suspension%5C%22%3Ecriticised%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20actions%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20CPR.%20Calling%20CPR%20%E2%80%9Cone%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20oldest%20and%20most%20esteemed%20policy%20research%20institutions%E2%80%9D%2C%20scholars%20had%20said%20it%20has%20a%20%E2%80%9Creputation%20for%20excellence%20that%20is%20second%20to%20none%20among%20international%20scholars%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20high%20court%20had%20earlier%20stayed%20the%20I-T%20Department%E2%80%99s%20proceedings%20against%20CPR%2C%20and%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20supported%20this%20stay.%20CPR%20had%20moved%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20of%20Delhi%20against%20the%20I-T%20department%E2%80%99s%20order%2C%20which%20sought%20to%20cancel%20its%20registration%20under%20Section%2012A%20with%20retrospective%20effect%2C%20thereby%20taking%20away%20its%20tax%20exemption%20status.%20The%20hearings%20in%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20on%20the%20matter%20are%20ongoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705478644000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F09%2F07154303%2FUntitled-design-4-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhome-ministry-cancels-centre-for-policy-researchs-fcra-registration%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCPR%20firmly%20reiterates%20that%20it%20is%20in%20complete%20compliance%20with%20the%20law%2C%20and%20has%20been%20cooperating%20fully%20and%20exhaustively%20at%20every%20step%20of%20the%20process.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhome-ministry-cancels-centre-for-policy-researchs-fcra-registration%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Seungkwan%20shares%20cover%20video%20featuring%20Moonbin%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705478499000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106922008%2Cimgsize-48974.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fk-pop%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fseventeens-seungkwan-shares-heartfelt-cover-video-featuring-personal-memories-of-astros-moonbin%2Farticleshow%2F106921880.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%2