0oversees%20thousands%20of%20veterinary%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBobi's%20age%20is%20registered%20in%20Portugal's%20government%20database%2C%20which%20Guinness%20World%20Records%20said%20it%20checked%20before%20giving%20out%20the%20award.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20an%20investigation%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2Fstory%2Fbobi-worlds-oldest-dog-fraud%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eby%20WIRED%20%3C%2Fa%3Ereported%20that%20an%20official%20said%20the%20database%20entry%20was%20based%20on%20information%20provided%20by%20Costa%2C%20the%20dog's%20owner.%20The%20outlet%20wrote%20multiple%20times%20that%20Costa%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20its%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBobi's%20record%20came%20just%20after%20Spike%2C%20a%2023-year-old%20Chihuahua%2C%20was%20named%20the%20oldest%20living%20dog%20by%20the%20Guinness%20World%20Records.%20Two%20weeks%20after%20Spike's%20record%20was%20announced%2C%20Bobi%20dethroned%20the%20Chihuahua.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPer%20the%20AP%2C%20Guinness%20World%20Records's%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20organization%20was%20aware%20of%20the%20public%20skepticism%20toward%20Bobi's%20record%20and%20that%20it%20received%20notes%20from%20veterinarians%20concerned%20about%20the%20validity%20of%20his%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2024%2Fjan%2F16%2Fworlds-oldest-dog-title-suspended-claim-investigated-bobi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Bobi's%20title%20was%20suspended%2C%20not%20taken%20away%20from%20him%2C%20as%20%26quot%3Bno%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20about%20any%20record%20holders%20yet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Bobi's%20record%20is%20stripped%20from%20him%2C%20the%20accolade%20of%20the%20world's%20oldest-ever%20dog%20would%20return%20to%20Bluey%2C%20an%20Australian%20cattle%20dog%20who%20lived%20to%2029%20years%20and%20five%20months%20old%20from%201910%20to%201939%2C%20per%20the%20Guinness%20Wo