27%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-gives-new-demos-for-vision-pro-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Dollar%20Ranks%20Last%20In%20World's%2010%20Strongest%20Currency%20List.%20India%20At...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECurrency%20is%20considered%20the%20lifeblood%20of%20global%20trade%20and%20reflects%20a%20country's%20economic%20vitality.%20The%20strength%20of%20a%20currency%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20a%20country's%20stability%20and%20robust%20financial%20health.%20As%20it%20surges%2C%20so%20does%20confidence%20in%20its%20economy%2C%20attracting%20investments%20and%20fostering%20international%20partnerships.%20A%20strong%20currency%20empowers%20nations%20to%20weather%20economic%20storms%2C%20fortifying%20their%20position%20in%20the%20interconnected%20web%20of%20global%20commerce.%20The%20United%20Nations%20officially%20recognises%20180%20currencies%20across%20the%20world%20as%20legal%20tender.%20Some%20currencies%20are%20popular%20and%20used%20widely%2C%20but%20these%20factors%20do%20not%20necessarily%20determine%20their%20value%20or%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrency%20strength%20is%20a%20delicate%20dance%20of%20supply%20and%20demand%2C%20influenced%20by%20factors%20ranging%20from%20interest%20rates%20and%20inflation%20to%20geopolitical%20stability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20robust%20currency%20not%20only%20enhances%20a%20country's%20purchasing%20power%20but%20also%20underlines%20its%20credibility%20on%20the%20world%20stage.%20Investors%20seek%20refuge%20in%20currencies%20that%20stand%20firm%2C%20creating%20a%20ripple%20effect%20that%20shapes%20financial%20markets%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbesindia.com%2Farticle%2Fexplainers%2Fhighest-valued-currencies-world%2F85581%2F1%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EForbes%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20released%20a%20list%20of%2010%20strongest%20currencies%20in%20the%20world%20(compared%20the%20Indian%20Rupee%20as%20well%20as%20USD)%2C%20along%20with%20the%20factors%20that%20contribute%20to%20their%20prominence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20in%20the%20list%20is%20the%20Kuwaiti%20Dinar%2C%20said%20Forbes.%20One%20Kuwaiti%20Dinar%20is%20equal%20to%20Rs%20270.23%20and%20%243.25.%20Next%20comes%20The%20Bahraini%20Dinar%2C%20which%20is%20valued%20at%20Rs%20220.4%20and%20%242.65.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENext%20it%20the%20list%20is%20Omani%20Rial%20(Rs%20215.84%20and%20%242.60)%2C%20followed%20by%20Jordanian%20Dinar%20(Rs%20117.10%20and%20%241.141)%2C%20Gibraltar%20Pound%20(Rs%20105.52%20and%20%241.27)%2C%20British%20Pound%20(Rs%20105.54%20and%20%241.27)%2C%20Cayman%20Island%20Dollar%20(Rs%2099.76%20and%20%241.20)%2C%20Swiss%20Franc%20(Rs%2097.54%20and%20%241.17)%20and%20the%20Euro%20(Rs%2090.80%20and%20%241.09).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20US%20Dollar%20is%20last%20on%20the%20list%2C%20with%20one%20USD%20valued%20at%20Rs%2083.10.%20Explaining%20the%20ranking%2C%20Forbes%20said%20that%20US%20Dollar%20is%20the%20most%20widely%20traded%20currency%20globally%20and%20holds%20the%20position%20as%20the%20primary%20reserve%20currency.%20Despite%20its%20popularity%2C%20it%20ranks%2010th%20among%20the%20world's%20strongest%20currencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Wednesday's%20exchange%20rate%20published%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.imf.org%2Fexternal%2Fnp%2Ffin%2Fdata%2Frms_rep.aspx%5C%22%3EInternational%20Monetary%20Fund's%20(IMF)%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20India%20ranks%2015%20with%20value%20listed%20as%2082.9%20per%20US%20Dollar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuwaiti%20Dinar%2C%20which%20holds%20the%20pole%20position%2C%20has%20consistently%20ranked%20as%20the%20world's%20most%20valuable%20currency%20since%20the%20time%20it%20was%20introduced%20in%201960.%20The%20reason%20behind%20the%20success%20of%20the%20currency%20is%20Kuwait's%20economic%20stability%2C%20which%20is%20driven%20by%20its%20oil%20reserves%20and%20tax-free%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EForbes%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Swiss%20Franc%2C%20the%20currency%20of%20Switzerland%20and%20Liechtenstein%2C%20is%20widely%20regarded%20as%20the%20most%20stable%20currency%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20is%20based%20on%20currency%20values%20till%20January%2010%2C%202024%2C%20and%20has%20been%20released%20with%20a%20disclaimer%20that%20these%20values%20are%20subject%20to%20fluctuation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705476420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-10%2Figl1kpc_global-currencies-reuters_625x300_23_October_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fus-dollar-ranks-last-in-worlds-10-strongest-currency-list-india-at-4878641%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20robust%20currency%20not%20only%20enhances%20a%20country's%20purchasing%20power%20but%20also%20underlines%20its%20credibility%20on%20the%20world%20stage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fus-dollar-ranks-last-in-worlds-10-strongest-currency-list-india-at-4878641%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fus-dollar-ranks-last-in-worlds-10-strongest-currency-list-india-at-4878641%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fus-dollar-ranks-last-in-worlds-10-strongest-currency-list-india-at-4878641%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gaza%20war%3A%20How%20South%20Africa's%20genocide%20case%20against%20Israel%20is%20shaping%20up%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705476352000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106921094%2Cimgsize-1110940.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fgaza-war-south-africas-genocide-case-against-israel-at-icj%2Farticleshow%2F106920913.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%