0analysis%20said%2C%20was%20at%20best%20a%20%26quot%3Bmarginal%20hypersonic%20missile.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlthough%20Russia%20calls%20the%20'Dagger'%20a%20hypersonic%20missile%2C%20analysts%20from%20other%20countries%20generally%20believe%20that%20the%20so-called%20hypersonic%20'Dagger'%20missile%20is%20actually%20an%20air-launched%20version%20of%20the%20'Iskander'%20short-range%20tactical%20ballistic%20missile%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20assessment%20aligns%20with%20what%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpatriot-kill-shot-impressive-russian-kinzhal-hypersonic-ballistic-missile-experts-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWestern%20experts%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20said%20about%20the%20Kinzhal%20%E2%80%94%20that%20it's%20not%20a%20%26quot%3Btrue%26quot%3B%20hypersonic%20missile%20in%20that%20it%20can%20reach%20hypersonic%20velocity%20but%20can't%20glide%20and%20maneuver%20effectively%20at%20such%20speeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20'Dagger'%20missile%20has%20more%20than%20enough%20ambition%20but%20not%20enough%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20July%20analysis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'The%20accuracy%20is%20unsatisfactory'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20November%20analysis%2C%20Yin%20blamed%20more%20than%20just%20a%20lack%20of%20sophistication%20in%20the%20Kinzhal%2C%20pointing%20to%20circumstances%20in%20the%20Russian%20military%20apparatus%20as%20a%20whole.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYin%20noted%20that%20Russia%20had%20stopped%20launching%20Kinzhals%20from%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-mig-31-russian-jet-2017-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMig-31s%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20choosing%20to%20instead%20use%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-says-it-shot-down-3-russian-su-34-jets-possibly-using-patriot-missiles-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESu-34%20jets%3C%2Fa%3E%20firing%20safely%20from%20outside%20the%20range%20of%20Ukraine's%20defenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20analyst%20wrote%20that%20the%20Su-34%20was%20proving%20too%20sluggish%20to%20fire%20the%20Kinzhal%20at%20an%20optimal%20speed.%20Already%20slower%20than%20the%20Mig-31%2C%20the%20Su-34%20was%20further%20weighed%20down%20by%20the%20heavy%20Kinzhal%2C%20Yin%20assessed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Russian%20servicemen%20repair%20a%20Su-34%20at%20an%20airbase%20in%20Syria.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a64ea243bb77284b9d3983%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERussian%20servicemen%20repairing%20a%20Su-34%20at%20an%20airbase%20in%20Syria.%3Cp%3EVASILY%20MAXIMOV%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20Kinzhal%20to%20be%20most%20efficient%2C%20the%20launch%20aircraft%20has%20to%20move%20at%20high%20speeds%20and%20altitudes%20to%20give%20the%20missile%20a%20proper%20range%20boost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTherefore%2C%20after%20the%20aircraft%20is%20equipped%20with%20the%20KH-47M2%20'Dagger%2C'%20excessive%20and%20unrealistic%20expectations%20cannot%20be%20placed%20on%20its%20initial%20capabilities%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20author%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20criticized%20Russia's%20satellite%20system%20for%20guiding%20the%20missiles%2C%20saying%20it%20didn't%20have%20enough%20satellites%20for%20precision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20accuracy%20is%20unsatisfactory%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20analyst%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYin%20then%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20Russia%20simply%20not%20having%20enough%20Kinzhals%2C%20saying%20Western%20sanctions%20had%20hobbled%20Moscow's%20capacity%20to%20quickly%20manufacture%20the%20weapons%2C%20which%20limited%20how%20the%20missiles%20could%20be%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20'Dagger'%20was%20not%20produced%20and%20equipped%20in%20large%20quantities.%20After%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20of%20expenditure%2C%20the