%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20underplayed%20the%20significance%20of%20him%20being%20on%20the%20bench%20that%20gave%20the%20notorious%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-ayodhya-verdict-possession%5C%22%3EAyodhya%20verdict%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20November%209%2C%202019.%20Many%20have%20called%20it%20out%20as%20an%20order%20grounded%20less%20in%20legal%20and%20constitutional%20points%20but%20more%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20placate%20a%20majoritarian%20agenda%20%E2%80%93%20one%20that%20is%20also%20advocated%20aggressively%20by%20both%20Modi%20and%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%206%2C%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fahmedabad%2Fafter-temple-visits-cji-flags-dhwaja-of-justice-to-district-court-lawyers-9098282%2F%5C%22%3Eendorsed%3C%2Fa%3E%20saffron%20flags%20flying%20atop%20temples%20as%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20flags%20of%20justice%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20offering%20prayers%20at%20the%20temples%20of%20Dwarikadhish%20and%20Somnath%20with%20his%20family%20in%20Gujarat%20last%20week%2C%20the%20CJI%20had%20no%20qualms%20in%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20inspired%20this%20morning%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3Edhwaja%3C%2Fem%3E%20(flag)%20at%20Dwarikadhish%20ji%2C%20very%20similar%20to%20the%20dhwaja%2C%20which%20I%20saw%20at%20Jagannath%20Puri.%20But%20look%20at%20this%20universality%20of%20the%20tradition%20in%20our%20nation%2C%20which%20binds%20all%20of%20us%20together.%20This%20dhwaja%20has%20a%20special%20meaning%20for%20us.%20And%20that%20meaning%20which%20the%20dhwaja%20gives%20us%20is%20%E2%80%93%20there%20is%20some%20unifying%20force%20above%20all%20of%20us%2C%20as%20lawyers%2C%20as%20judges%2C%20as%20citizens.%20And%20that%20unifying%20force%20is%20our%20humanity%2C%20which%20is%20governed%20by%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20by%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20all%20the%20above%20referred%20temples%20fly%20saffron%2Fyellow%20flags%20atop%20their%20structures.%20This%20is%20bound%20to%20raise%20deep%20concerns%20if%20CJI%20Chandrachud%2C%20by%20these%20much%20publicised%20remarks%2C%20was%20implying%20that%20the%20tricolour%20or%20the%20Indian%20national%20flag%20was%20not%20the%20%E2%80%9Cunifying%20force%E2%80%9D%20for%20Indians%20as%20were%20the%20flags%20that%20fly%20atop%20temples%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERSS%20accepted%20the%20tricolour%20only%20in%202002%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI%E2%80%99s%20statement%20has%20to%20be%20weighed%20against%20the%20context%20of%20the%20tricolour%20being%20chosen%20as%20the%20flag%20of%20free%2C%20independent%20and%20secular%20India.%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20CJI%20was%2C%20knowingly%20or%20unknowingly%2C%20rephrasing%20the%20statement%20of%20the%20most%20prominent%20ideologue%20of%20RSS%2C%20M.S.%20Golwalkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGowalkar%2C%20while%20addressing%20a%20Gurupurnima%20gathering%20in%20Nagpur%20on%20July%2014%2C%201946%2C%20had%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20the%20saffron%20flag%20which%20in%20totality%20represented%20Bhartiya%20(Indian)%20culture.%20It%20was%20the%20embodiment%20of%20God.%20We%20firmly%20believe%20that%20in%20the%20end%20the%20whole%20nation%20will%20bow%20before%20this%20saffron%20flag.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20denouncing%20the%20choice%20of%20the%20tricolour%20as%20the%20national%20flag%2C%20he%20said%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.counterview.net%2F2021%2F02%2Fgolwalkars-views-on-tricolour-martyrs.html%5C%22%3Eessay%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%98Drifting%20and%20Drifting%E2%80%99%3Cem%3E%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0in%20the%20book%20%3Cem%3EBunch%20of%20Thoughts%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%9COur%20leaders%20have%20set%20up%20a%20new%20flag%20for%20our%20country.%20Why%20did%20they%20do%20so%3F%20It%20is%20just%20a%20case%20of%20drifting%20and%20imitating%E2%80%A6%20Ours%20is%20an%20ancient%20and%20great%20nation%20with%20a%20glorious%20past.%20Then%2C%20had%20we%20no%20flag%20of%20our%20own%3F%20Had%20we%20no%20national%20emblem%20at%20all%20these%20thousands%20of%20years%3F%20Undoubtedly%2C%20we%20had.%20Then%20why%20this%20utter%20void%2C%20this%20utter%20vacuum%20in%20our%20minds%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20seminal%20hatred%20for%20the%20tricolour%20even%20led%20the%20RSS%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fhow-the-hindu-right-opposed-the-national-flag-and-the-quit-india-movement%5C%22%3Edeclare%20the%20tricolour%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20%E2%80%98evil%E2%80%99%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20independence.%20The%20RSS%E2%80%99s%20English%20language%20mouthpiece%2C%20%3Cem%3EOrganiser%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20demeaning%20the%20choice%20of%20the%20national%20flag%2C%20wrote%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20people%20who%20have%20come%20to%20power%20by%20the%20kick%20of%20fate%20may%20give%20in%20our%20hands%20the%20tricolour%20but%20it%20never%20be%20respected%20and%20owned%20by%20Hindus.%20The%20word%20three%20is%20in%20itself%20an%20evil%2C%20and%20a%20flag%20having%20three%20colours%20will%20certainly%20produce%20a%20very%20bad%20psychological%20effect%20and%20is%20injurious%20to%20a%20country.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RSS%20borrowed%20this%20hatred%20for%20the%20tricolour%20from%20V.D.%20Savarkar%20who%20declared%20that%20%E2%80%9CThe%20%3Cem%3ECharkha%3C%2Fem%3E-Flag%20(then%20the%20tricolour%20used%20to%20have%20a%20charkha%20or%20a%20spinning%20wheel%20in%20the%20middle%2C%20which%20was%20later%20replaced%20by%20the%20Ashok%20Chakra)%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20may%20very%20well%20represent%20a%20Khadi-Bhandar%2C%20but%20the%20charkha%20can%20never%20symbolise%20and%20represent%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20proud%20and%20ancient%20nation%20like%20the%20Hindus.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20cause%20for%20concern%20that%20the%20CJI%2C%20who%20is%20duty-bound%20to%20safeguard%20the%20democratic-secular%20polity%20of%20India%2C%20which%20the%20tricolour%20so%20evocatively%20embodies%2C%20appeared%20to%20be%20chiming%20more%20with%20those%20who%20protested%20the%20tricolour%20for%20decades%20before%20accepting%20it%20grudgingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EShamsul%20Islam%20is%20an%20activist%2C%20author%2C%20and%20theatre%20person%20based%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705410039000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F08110652%2FGDI_UsnWYAA-QMc.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fwhy-cji-chandrachuds-statement-on-the-saffron-dhwaja-as-a-unifying-symbol-raises-red-flags%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20endorsement%20of%20the%20saffron%20%E2%80%98dhwajas%E2%80%99%20fluttering%20atop%20Gujarat%E2%80%99s%20temples%20relay%20a%20worrying%20message%20from%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud.%20There%20is%20context%20here%20which%20must%20be%20flagged.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A25%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fwhy-cji-chandrachuds-statement-on-the-saffron-dhwaja-as-a-unifying-symbol-raises-red-flags%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Unrelenting%20Struggles%20of%20Punjab's%20Kinnow%20Farmers%20Amidst%20a%20Bumper%20Crop%20This%20Year%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F13125046%2Fagriculture-copy.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EPunjab%20is%20the%20leading%20state%20for%20its%20cultivation%20of%20kinnow%2C%20a%20high-yielding%20mandarin%20(a%20hybrid%20plant)%2C%20with%20an%20average%20cultivation%20area%20of%2059%2C000%20hectares.%20The%20town%20of%20Abohar%20in%20the%20Fazilka%20district%20alone%20contributes%2060%25%20to%20the%20overall%20state%20production.%20The%20harvesting%20season%20for%20this%20fruit%20commences%20in%20December%2C%20and%20continues%20till%20March%2C%20with%20the%20peak%20yield%20observed%20during%20January%20and%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%E2%80%99s%20kinnow%20harvest%20has%20been%20exceptional%2C%20due%20to%20favourable%20temperatures%20during%20the%20crop%E2%80%99s%20flowering%20stage%2C%20resulting%20in%20an%20anticipated%20output%20of%2013.5%20lakh%20metric%20tonnes.%20However%2C%20this%20bumper%20harvest%20has%20led%20to%20a%20significant%20decline%20in%20farm%20gate%20prices.%20The%20farm%20gate%20value%20of%20a%20cultivated%20product%20in%20agriculture%20is%20the%20market%20value%20of%20a%20product%20minus%20the%20selling%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fruit%20used%20to%20fetch%20Rs%2020-30%20per%20kilogram.%20However%2C%20this%20year%2C%20farmers%20are%20getting%20only%20Rs%206-12%20per%20kg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuccessive%20state%20governments%20had%20been%20dilly-dallying%20on%20the%20implementation%20of%20several%20crop%20diversification%20measures%2C%20and%20consequently%2C%20wheat-paddy%20monoculture%20is%20going%20on%20in%20the%20state%20unabated.%20While%20kinnow%20cultivation%20has%20been%20promoted%20as%20a%20competitive%20cropping%20alternative%20for%20farmers%20in%20southwest%20Punjab%2C%20the%20precarious%20pricing%20dynamics%20and%20weak%20institutional%20arrangements%20associated%20with%20it%20may%20not%20counter%20the%20dominance%20of%20a%20wheat-paddy%20monoculture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEconomic%20viability%20of%20kinnow%20cultivation%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20farmer%20will%20diversify%20from%20paddy%20to%20other%20crops%20if%20the%20returns%20are%20not%20only%20promising%20but%20also%20significantly%20higher%20than%20those%20from%20paddy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20assessed%20the%20cultivation%20practices%20of%20kinnow%20and%20calculated%20the%20operational%20cost%20per%20acre%20based%20on%20the%20interactions%20with%20farmers%20from%20Jandwala%20village%20in%20Abohar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKinnow%20cultivation%20is%20quite%20laborious%20throughout%20the%20crop%20cycle%20and%20depends%20heavily%20on%20both%20hired%20and%20family%20labour.%20As%20compared%20to%20wheat%20and%20paddy%2C%20this%20crop%20is%20quite%20fragile%20as%20it%20requires%20the%20family%20labour%20to%20continuously%20micro-manage%20crop%20safety%20during%20and%20before%20the%20harvesting%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStrenuous%20farm%20operations%20generally%20favour%20male%20labour%2C%20while%20for%20tasks%20such%20as%20tilling%20the%20soil%20and%20harvesting%2C%20female%20labour%20is%20preferred%2C%20as%20they%20do%20the%20work%20very%20neatly%20and%20are%20also%20available%20at%20lesser%20wage%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFarm%20operations%20based%20on%20labour%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ctable%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ctbody%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2235%25%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFarm%20Operations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2235%25%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMechanism%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2229%25%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHired%20labour%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E(Male%2FFemale)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2235%25%5C%22%3EPreparing%20the%20field%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2235%25%5C%22%3ELeveller%2C%20Rotavator%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2229%25%5C%22%3EOne%20Male%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2235%25%5C%22%3EPlanting%20the%20saplings%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2235%25%5C%22%3EManual%20and%20Machinery%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2229%25%5C%22%3ETwo%20Male%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2235%25%5C%22%3EIrrigation%20Doses%20(two)%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2235%25%5C%22%3EDrip%2FFlood%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2229%25%5C%22%3EOne%20Male%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2235%25%5C%22%3EFilling%20of%20cracks%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2235%25%5C%22%3EManually%20with%20hand%20tools%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2229%25%5C%22%3EOne%20Male%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2235%25%5C%22%3ESpraying%20fertilisers%20and%20pesticides%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2235%25%5C%22%3EManually%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2229%25%5C%22%3EOne%20Male%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2235%25%5C%22%3EPruning%20of%20trees%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2235%25%5C%22%3EDone%20twice%20a%20year%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2229%25%5C%22%3EOne%20Male%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2235%25%5C%22%3ETilling%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2235%25%5C%22%3EDone%20thrice%20a%20year%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2229%25%5C%22%3EFour%20Female%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2235%25%5C%22%3EHarvesting%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2235%25%5C%22%3EManually%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%20width%3D%5C%2229%25%5C%22%3EBoth%20Female%20and%20Male%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESource%3A%20Primary%20survey%2C%202023%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incubation%20period%2C%20from%20three%20to%20four%20years%2C%20and%20the%20wear%20and%20tear%20of%20the%20plants%20are%20inseparable%20parts%20of%20the%20cultivation%20cost.%20The%20overall%20cost%20of%20cultivating%20kinnow%20per%20acre%20is%20Rs%2047%2C000.%20The%20average%20yield%20from%20a%20kinnow%20farm%20is%20100%20quintals%20per%20acre%2C%20with%20an%20average%20farm%20gate%20price%20of%20Rs%20700%20per%20quintal%20this%20year.%20Consequently%2C%20returns%20per%20acre%20amount%20to%20Rs%2070%2C000%2C%20and%20net%20returns%20over%20operational%20costs%20are%20Rs%2023%2C000%20per%20acre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComparatively%2C%20last%20year%E2%80%99s%20average%20price%20of%20Rs%202%2C500%20per%20quintal%20resulted%20in%20net%20returns%20of%20Rs%202.03%20lakh%20per%20acre.%20This%20demonstrates%20significant%20price%20variations%20and%20fluctuations%20in%20profit%20margins.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20paddy%2C%20with%20an%20average%20cost%20of%20Rs%2020%2C000%20per%20acre%2C%20yields%20net%20returns%20of%20around%20Rs%2045%2C000%20per%20acre.%20Paddy%20is%20a%20stable%20crop%20for%20farmers%2C%20with%20fewer%20fluctuations%20in%20returns%20due%20to%20open-ended%20procurement%20by%20the%20government%20with%20a%20minimum%20support%20price%20(MSP)%20and%20its%20weather%20resilience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20paddy%20is%20a%20relatively%20less%20labour-intensive%20crop.%20It%20does%20not%20require%20any%20micro-management%20as%20the%20harvesting%20is%20fully%20mechanised.%20This%20makes%20paddy%20an%20obvious%20choice%20for%20the%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F16161052%2Fimage-1747.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22603%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F16161052%2Fimage-1747.png%20603w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F16161052%2Fimage-1747-300x130.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693228%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22262%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESource%3A%20Primary%20survey%2C%202023%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMarket%20fluctuations%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20bearing%20high%20investments%20in%20kinnow%20production%2C%20farmers%20have%20to%20face%20market%20asymmetries%20each%20year.%20Over%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20effective%20post-harvest%20management%20for%20kinnow%20growers%20has%20been%20lacking.%20There%20is%20an%20absence%20of%20processing%20units%20to%20absorb%20local%20kinnow%20production.%20While%20several%20private%20waxing%20and%20grading%20plants%20have%20emerged%20in%20the%20area%2C%20thanks%20to%20traders%20and%20business%20entrepreneurs%2C%20there%20is%20currently%20no%20buyback%20guarantee%20or%20price%20surety%20for%20the%20produce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20existence%20of%20a%20well-established%20citrus%20%3Cem%3Emandi%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Abohar%2C%20it%20does%20not%20guarantee%20farmers%20a%20favourable%20price%2C%20even%20when%20factoring%20in%20the%20costs%20of%20transportation%2C%20loading%2C%20and%20unloading.%20Consequently%2C%20farmers%20find%20themselves%20heavily%20reliant%20on%20agents%20or%20contractors%20for%20marketing%20their%20produce.%20Given%20the%20perishable%20nature%20of%20the%20product%2C%20contractors%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20kinnow%20procurement%2C%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20price%20determination%20is%20largely%20dependent%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20contractors%20supply%20the%20fruit%20to%20other%20states%2C%20such%20as%20Delhi%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20and%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20The%20fruit%20is%20also%20supplied%20to%20other%20countries%2C%20such%20as%20Bangladesh%20and%20Nepal.%20Contracts%20are%20finalised%20in%20June%20and%20the%20rates%20are%20fixed%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20number%20of%20flowers%20on%20a%20tree%20that%20indicate%20the%20output%20of%20the%20fruit.%20These%20contracts%20are%20not%20directly%20established%20with%20the%20companies%2C%20but%20are%20intermediated%20through%20a%20number%20of%20agents%20who%20further%20market%20the%20fruit.%20Payments%20are%20directly%20transferred%20to%20the%20bank%20accounts%20of%20the%20farmers.%20In%20case%20of%20any%20delay%2C%20an%20extra%20amount%20is%20also%20paid.%20Agents%20bear%20the%20entire%20cost%20of%20picking%20the%20fruit%20from%20the%20farms%2C%20which%20includes%20loading%20and%20unloading%2C%20grading%20and%20waxing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESelling%20through%20contractors%20is%20found%20to%20be%20the%20most%20convenient%20marketing%20method%2C%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20prices%20offered%20by%20contractors%20are%20among%20the%20lowest%20across%20all%20marketing%20channels.%20As%20contractors%20form%20their%20cartel%20and%20prices%20are%20largely%20influenced%20by%20the%20market%20forces%2C%20it%20creates%20asymmetry%20of%20bargaining%20power%20in%20favour%20of%20buyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20farmers%20prefer%20contractors%20because%20of%20the%20prompt%20payment%20they%20provide.%20Many%20smallholders%20have%20expressed%20the%20need%20for%20immediate%20cash%20after%20the%20harvest%20to%20settle%20loans%20from%20commission%20agents%20and%20moneylenders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F16162556%2Fimage-1748.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22805%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F16162556%2Fimage-1748.png%20558w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F16162556%2Fimage-1748-300x118.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693234%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22316%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESource%3A%20Primary%20Survey%2C%202023%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHence%2C%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20proper%20governance%20over%20an%20assured%20marketing%20system%20and%20value%20chain%2C%20kinnow%20has%20remained%20a%20risky%20investment%20for%20small%20growers%2C%20even%20when%20there%20is%20a%20niche%20demand%20within%20and%20outside%20Indian%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20way%20forward%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20structure%20of%20kinnow%20cultivation%20suggests%20that%20it%20requires%20relatively%20more%20investment%20on%20labour%2C%20machinery%2C%20micro-management%2C%20and%20skill-level.%20As%20compared%20to%20paddy%2C%20the%20opportunity%20cost%20of%20establishing%20a%20kinnow%20farm%20is%20relatively%20higher.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20risky%20affair%20to%20venture%20in%2C%20especially%20for%20small%20holders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHence%2C%20paddy%20is%20an%20obvious%20choice%20for%20the%20farmers%20in%20Punjab%2C%20as%20there%20are%20no%20economically%20stable%20and%20rewarding%20alternatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Punjab%20has%20been%20the%20top%20contributor%20of%20paddy%20in%20the%20central%20pool%20of%20food%20grains%20for%20the%20last%20ten%20years.%20Hence%2C%20blaming%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20farmers%20for%20cultivating%20paddy%20and%20its%20consequential%20impact%20on%20the%20environment%2C%20especially%20during%20the%20seasonal%20rise%20in%20air%20pollution%20in%20Delhi%2C%20is%20a%20classic%20case%20of%20the%20pot%20calling%20the%20kettle%20black.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20several%20measures%20need%20to%20be%20taken%20to%20safeguard%20kinnow%20growers.%20The%20agro%20food%20industry%20should%20be%20given%20priority%20to%20absorb%20the%20produce%20locally.%20Building%20relationships%20with%20food%20processors%2C%20juice%20manufacturers%2C%20and%20other%20agribusinesses%20can%20create%20a%20stable%20market%20for%20kinnow%20growers.%20Additionally%2C%20small%20and%20marginal%20farmers%20need%20hand-holding%20support%20from%20the%20government%20to%20diversify.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENivedita%20Sharma%20is%20assistant%20professor%20at%20the%20Council%20for%20Social%20Development%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20Gurpreet%20Singh%20is%20assistant%20professor%20at%20the%20Jindal%20School%20of%20Government%20and%20Public%20Policy%2C%20O.P.%20Jindal%20Global%20University%2C%20Sonipat%20in%20Haryana.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705408245000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F13125046%2Fagriculture-copy.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fwhy-punjabs-farmers-have-opted-for-paddy-over-kinnow-despite-a-bumper-crop-harvest%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22High%20operational%20costs%2C%20market%20uncertainties%2C%20and%20ineffective%20institutional%20support%20make%20kinnow%20farming%20a%20risky%20venture%2C%20pushing%20farmers%20to%20choose%20paddy%20cultivation%2C%20which%20is%20considered%20a%20stable%20option%20for%20them%2C%20despite%20the%20environmental%20challenges%20associated%20with%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fwhy-punjabs-farmers-have-opted-for-paddy-over-kinnow-despite-a-bumper-crop-harvest%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Supreme%20Court%20Puts%20Mathura%20Mosque%20Survey%20Proceedings%20on%20Hold%20for%20Now%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F07141300%2FKashi-gyanvapi_1-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Tuesday%20put%20a%20stay%20on%20the%20execution%20of%20a%20recent%20order%20passed%20by%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20allowing%20an%20application%20to%20appoint%20an%20advocate%20commission%20to%20survey%20the%20Shahi%20Idgah%20Masjid%20adjoining%20the%20Krishna%20Janmabhoomi%20Temple%20in%20Mathura.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20put%20a%20temporary%20hold%20on%20the%20proceedings%20in%20the%20high%20court%20a%20day%20before%20the%20latter%20was%20scheduled%20to%20hear%20arguments%20on%20the%20composition%20and%20modalities%20of%20the%20advocate%20commission%20survey%20at%20the%20Mughal-era%20mosque.%20The%20high%20court%20had%20on%20December%2014%2C%202023%20allowed%20the%20application%20of%20the%20Hindu%20plaintiffs%20demanding%20an%20advocate%20commission%20to%20survey%20the%20Shahi%20Idgah%20Masjid.%20The%20plaintiffs%20claimed%20there%20were%20a%20number%20of%20signs%20of%20Hindu%20religion%20on%20the%20structure%20of%20the%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20management%20committee%20of%20the%20trust%20taking%20care%20of%20the%20Shahi%20Idgah%20Masjid%20filed%20a%20Special%20Leave%20Petition%20(Civil)%20against%20the%20high%20court%20order.%20Hearing%20the%20matter%20on%20January%2016%2C%20a%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20Dipankar%20Datta%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20issued%20notice%20in%20the%20matter%20and%20said%20the%20proceedings%20before%20the%20high%20court%20could%20continue%20but%20the%20commission%20survey%20would%20not%20be%20executed%20till%20the%20next%20day%20of%20hearing%2C%20January%2023%2C%20said%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fsc-allahabad-hc-order-shahi-idgah-mosque-survey-mathura-9111182%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20quoted%20the%20judges%20saying%20that%20the%20application%20filed%20before%20the%20high%20court%20by%20the%20plaintiffs%20seeking%20an%20advocate%20commission%20was%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20vague%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCan%20an%20application%20be%20made%20like%20this%3F%20We%20have%20reservations%20about%20the%20application.%20Look%20at%20the%20prayer.%20It%E2%80%99s%20so%20vague.%20Read%20it.%20You%20cannot%20make%20an%20omnibus%20application%20like%20this.%20You%20have%20to%20be%20very%20clear%20about%20what%20you%20want%20the%20local%20commissioner%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Khanna%20said%2C%20reported%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20detailed%20written%20order%20of%20the%20hearing%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20uploaded%20on%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20total%20of%2018%20suits%20filed%20by%20plaintiffs%20seeking%20removal%20of%20the%20Shahi%20Idgah%20Mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%2011%2C%20the%20high%20court%20decided%20to%20consolidate%2015%20out%20of%20the%2018%20suits%20filed%20in%20the%20matter.%20Justice%20Mayank%20Kumar%20Jain%20passed%20the%20order%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20relief%20claimed%20in%20these%2015%20suits%20numbered%201%2C%202%2C%204%2C%205%2C%206%2C%207%2C%208%2C%209%2C%2011%2C%2012%2C%2013%2C%2014%2C%2015%2C%2016%20and%2018%20were%20similar.%20The%20judge%20said%20the%20proceedings%20in%20these%20suits%20may%20be%20decided%20simultaneously%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20common%20evidence.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20save%20the%20time%20of%20the%20Court%2C%20the%20expenses%20to%20be%20incurred%20to%20the%20parties%2C%20and%20to%20avoid%20conflicting%20judgments%20it%20appears%20expedient%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20justice%20to%20consolidate%20the%20suits%20with%20each%20other%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Jain%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20made%20the%20suit%20titled%20%3Cem%3EBhagwan%20Shri%20Krishan%20Virajman%20at%20Katra%20Keshav%20Dev%20Khewat%20No.%20255%20and%20others%20Vs.%20U.P.%20Sunni%20Central%20Waqf%20Board%20through%20Chairman%20and%20others%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0as%20the%20leading%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20is%20being%20argued%20by%20pro-Hindutva%20lawyer%20Hari%20Shankar%20Jain%2C%20who%20was%20involved%20in%20both%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20and%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20cases%20and%20was%20in%202014%20felicitated%20by%20the%20BJP%20for%20filing%20cases%20against%20the%20then%20Samajwadi%20Party-led%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2014%2C%20while%20allowing%20the%20application%20for%20an%20advocate%20commission%2C%20Justice%20Jain%20observed%20that%20by%20appointment%20of%20a%20panel%20of%20three%20advocates%20as%20commission%2C%20neither%20side%20would%20suffer%20any%20harm%20or%20injury%2C%20as%20the%20commissioner%20report%20does%20not%20affect%20the%20merits%20of%20the%20case.%20During%20the%20course%20of%20the%20survey%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Csanctity%20of%20the%20campus%20can%20be%20directed%20to%20be%20maintained%20strictly%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20no%20harm%20or%20injury%20be%20caused%20to%20the%20structure%20in%20any%20manner%2C%20the%20judge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commission%20would%20also%20submit%20its%20report%20on%20the%20alleged%20existence%20of%20particular%20Hindu%20signs%20in%20the%20mosque%2C%20as%20alleged%20by%20the%20plaintiffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plaintiffs%20have%20claimed%20that%20the%20place%20of%20birth%20of%20Lord%20Krishna%20lies%20beneath%20the%20mosque%20and%20that%20there%20were%20a%20%E2%80%9Cnumber%20of%20signs%E2%80%9D%20that%20established%20that%20the%20structure%20of%20the%20mosque%20was%20a%20Hindu%20temple.%20The%20plaintiffs%20submitted%20the%20following%20in%20court%3A%20the%20kalash%20and%20pinnacle%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20mosque%20exemplify%20Hindu%20architectural%20style%20and%20are%20not%20present%20in%20any%20Islamic%20structure%3B%20a%20pillar%20with%20a%20lotus%20shaped%20top%2C%20a%20characteristic%20of%20Hindu%20temples%2C%20exists%20above%20the%20main%20gate%20of%20the%20mosque%3B%20the%20image%20of%20Hindu%20deity%20Sheshnaag%2C%20who%20Hindus%20believe%20protected%20Lord%20Krishna%20on%20the%20night%20of%20his%20birth%2C%20is%20etched%20on%20the%20wall%20of%20the%20structure%3B%20there%20are%20visible%20Hindu%20religious%20symbols%20and%20engravings%20at%20the%20base%20of%20the%20pillar%20of%20the%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UP%20Sunni%20Central%20Waqf%20Board%20dismissed%20these%20claims%2C%20arguing%20that%20the%20Shahi%20Idgah%20Mosque%20does%20not%20fall%20within%20the%20ambit%20of%20the%2013.37%20acres%20land%20at%20Katra%20Keshav%20Dev%20and%20that%20the%20birth%20place%20of%20Lord%20Krishna%20does%20not%20lie%20beneath%20the%20mosque.%20They%20categorically%20denied%20that%20designs%20in%20Mughal%20architecture%20of%20the%20mosque%20resemble%20Hindu%20religious%20symbols%20or%20establish%20that%20the%20Shahi%20Idgah%20Mosque%20was%20a%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubmitting%20that%20the%20claim%20of%20the%20plaintiffs%20was%20based%20on%20%E2%80%9Cguess%20work%E2%80%9D%20and%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20substantiated%20by%20any%20documentary%20evidence%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20mosque%20side%2C%20while%20objecting%20to%20a%20commission%20survey%2C%20said%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccourt%20cannot%20be%20made%20a%20tool%20to%20collect%20evidence%20for%E2%80%9D%20the%20plaintiffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20overruled%20these%20arguments%20to%20allow%20for%20a%20survey.%20Following%20the%20court%20order%2C%20counsel%20for%20the%20plaintiffs%20Vishnu%20Shankar%20Jain%20submitted%20an%20application%20pleading%20that%20the%20commission%20may%20be%20headed%20by%20a%20retired%20high%20court%20judge%20and%20that%20certain%20advocates%20on%20their%20behalf%20may%20also%20be%20permitted%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20proceedings%20of%20the%20commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20hearing%20on%20the%20modalities%20of%20the%20advocate%20commission%20was%20listed%20for%20January%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705407059000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F07141300%2FKashi-gyanvapi_1-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-puts-mathura-gyanvapi-mosque-survey-proceedings-on-hold-for-now%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20put%20a%20temporary%20hold%20on%20the%20proceedings%20in%20the%20high%20court%20a%20day%20before%20the%20latter%20was%20scheduled%20to%20hear%20arguments%20on%20the%20composition%20and%20modalities%20of%20the%20advocate%20commission%20survey%20at%20the%20Mughal-era%20mosque.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-puts-mathura-gyanvapi-mosque-survey-proceedings-on-hold-for-now%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cargo%20vessel%20'hit%20by%20missile'%20off%20Yemen%20coast%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705405320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F01%2F70